      { "author": { "uri": { "label": "https://itunes.apple.com/gb/reviews/id256598923" }, "name": { "label": "Db198335" }, "label": "" }, "updated": { "label": "2026-03-15T03:14:22-07:00" }, "im:rating": { "label": "4" }, "im:version": { "label": "1.210.0" }, "id": { "label": "13850259470" }, "title": { "label": "Good app - however" }, "content": { "label": "Great app however the personalised loan rate constantly flicks to a screen showing fetching your personalised rates and does not move beyond this which is very frustrating and does not seem to be getting fixed.", "attributes": { "type": "text" } }, "link": { "attributes": { "rel": "related", "href": "https://itunes.apple.com/gb/review?id=1324011914&type=Purple%20Software" } }, "im:voteSum": { "label": "0" }, "im:contentType": { "attributes": { "term": "Application", "label": "Application" } }, "im:voteCount": { "label": "0" } },
      { "author": { "uri": { "label": "https://itunes.apple.com/gb/reviews/id212108352" }, "name": { "label": "Jason bibby iPhone16" }, "label": "" }, "updated": { "label": "2026-03-13T03:23:50-07:00" }, "im:rating": { "label": "1" }, "im:version": { "label": "1.210.0" }, "id": { "label": "13843153440" }, "title": { "label": "Credit card" }, "content": { "label": "I was a victim of fraud someone cloned my card and spend 600 euros (im in the uk) I spoke with them about the situation they agreed was fraud and would clear the balance that was used, they only cleared 90% of the balance and I was left to clear the rest baring in mind it was 0 before my card was cloned, I’ve closed the account now", "attributes": { "type": "text" } }, "link": { "attributes": { "rel": "related", "href": "https://itunes.apple.com/gb/review?id=1324011914&type=Purple%20Software" } }, "im:voteSum": { "label": "0" }, "im:contentType": { "attributes": { "term": "Application", "label": "Application" } }, "im:voteCount": { "label": "0" } },
      { "author": { "uri": { "label": "https://itunes.apple.com/gb/reviews/id1878278819" }, "name": { "label": "sani3992" }, "label": "" }, "updated": { "label": "2026-03-12T13:43:00-07:00" }, "im:rating": { "label": "5" }, "im:version": { "label": "1.210.0" }, "id": { "label": "13841435861" }, "title": { "label": "Superb Bank service" }, "content": { "label": "best mobile banking services in uk", "attributes": { "type": "text" } }, "link": { "attributes": { "rel": "related", "href": "https://itunes.apple.com/gb/review?id=1324011914&type=Purple%20Software" } }, "im:voteSum": { "label": "0" }, "im:contentType": { "attributes": { "term": "Application", "label": "Application" } }, "im:voteCount": { "label": "0" } },
      { "author": { "uri": { "label": "https://itunes.apple.com/gb/reviews/id203626337" }, "name": { "label": "Thatenglishfellow" }, "label": "" }, "updated": { "label": "2026-03-11T15:30:19-07:00" }, "im:rating": { "label": "2" }, "im:version": { "label": "1.209.0" }, "id": { "label": "13838308512" }, "title": { "label": "Misleading marketing. Clunky app." }, "content": { "label": "The maximum Cashback you can earn each month is £2.50 (2% of £125 - that’s just £30 per year), and as Zopa doesn’t offer switching, you’ll have to spend hours manually transferring all your bills to this account. That alone makes it not worth the time and effort to set it up. \n\nThe linked 7.1% regular saver sounds excellent but is no better as it ‘matures’ after just 6 months, so the maximum interest you can earn is just £36. What could you buy for that, and is it worth waiting 6 months to get it ‘free’?  \n\nThe 2% interest on account balances IS good for a current account as of March 2026, but that is still much lower than inflation, (the rising cost of living) so any money left in it is effectively getting smaller not bigger. \n\nThe app itself is very basic and clunky, and lacks almost all of real time functionality and features common with most fintech challenger banks today. \n\nThis account has excellent headlines, but falls very short when you look at the fine print. Get one if you just want an extra account to put money for bills aside - if you can bare the hassle of transferring them manually, but DON’T keep your money in it if you have more than £300 left over each month to save.", "attributes": { "type": "text" } }, "link": { "attributes": { "rel": "related", "href": "https://itunes.apple.com/gb/review?id=1324011914&type=Purple%20Software" } }, "im:voteSum": { "label": "0" }, "im:contentType": { "attributes": { "term": "Application", "label": "Application" } }, "im:voteCount": { "label": "0" } },
